      <title>土耳其、保加利亚、罗马尼亚组建黑海扫雷部队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/turkey-bulgaria-romania-form-black-sea-mine-hunting-force</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其、罗马尼亚和保加利亚联手在黑海扫雷，此举旨在提高航运安全并支持至关重要的乌克兰谷物出口以获得资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/turkey-bulgaria-romania-form-black-sea-mine-hunting-force</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 05:05:14 GMT</pubDate>
