    <item>
      <title>法国秘密机构令全球投资者措手不及</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/investing-in-france-global-companies-blindsided-by-macron-s-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府表示希望吸引外国投资，但一些公司发现他们的计划被影响力过大的国家机构 Sisse 打乱了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/investing-in-france-global-companies-blindsided-by-macron-s-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 05:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚在程序陷入混乱后争夺欧盟最高职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/romania-vies-for-an-eu-top-job-after-process-thrown-into-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，罗马尼亚总统克劳斯·约翰尼斯正在寻求成为下一任欧洲理事会主席，该职位可能会因查尔斯·米歇尔出人意料地宣布将竞选议会席位而提前空出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/romania-vies-for-an-eu-top-job-after-process-thrown-into-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海莉和德桑蒂斯在爱荷华州党团会议前的最后一场共和党辩论中互相侮辱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/republican-debate-haley-desantis-attack-each-other-before-iowa-caucus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在爱荷华州党团会议之前的最后一场共和党辩论中，尼基·黑利和罗恩·德桑蒂斯立即发起攻击，无情地指责对方在问题上撒谎和反复无常。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/republican-debate-haley-desantis-attack-each-other-before-iowa-caucus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:59:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平呼吁稳定美国关系，应对台湾选举考验两国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/xi-calls-for-stable-us-relations-as-taiwan-election-tests-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平表示，中国希望与美国合作，改善世界最大经济体之间的关系——就在台湾大选前几天发表的言论可能会影响未来几年两国之间的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/xi-calls-for-stable-us-relations-as-taiwan-election-tests-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 03:38:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国放宽落地签证要求以促进旅游业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/china-relaxes-requirements-for-visa-on-arrival-to-boost-tourism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将放宽部分签证要求，以方便外国人商务、教育和旅游，此举是在政府寻求重振放缓的经济之际采取的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/china-relaxes-requirements-for-visa-on-arrival-to-boost-tourism</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 03:15:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷卡普托经纪人与他曾经与之抗争的国际货币基金组织达成交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/argentina-s-caputo-brokers-deal-with-the-imf-he-once-battled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路易斯·卡普托上次与国际货币基金组织谈判时，在如何管理阿根廷陷入困境的货币问题上存在激烈分歧，导致他辞去了该国央行行长的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/argentina-s-caputo-brokers-deal-with-the-imf-he-once-battled</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称中国可能是台湾领导人虚假视频的幕后黑手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/china-may-be-behind-fake-videos-of-taiwan-s-leader-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《台北时报》报道，中国可能要在台湾总统蔡英文的政党关键选举之前制作和发布大量虚假视频。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/china-may-be-behind-fake-videos-of-taiwan-s-leader-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 02:43:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相岸田成立改革小组以恢复支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/japan-prime-minister-kishida-launches-reform-panel-in-bid-to-restore-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄成立了一个特别工作组，改革执政党的金融交易，这是一项新的尝试，以恢复对因广泛丑闻而跌至历史低点的政府的支持率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/japan-prime-minister-kishida-launches-reform-panel-in-bid-to-restore-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 02:40:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格里芬和施瓦茨曼为麦考密克超级政治行动委员会提供了 1800 万美元的资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/griffin-schwarzman-fuel-mccormick-super-pac-s-18-million-haul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位熟悉该组织财务的人士透露，Citadel 的 Ken Griffin、Blackstone 的 Steve Schwarzman 和 Elliott Management 的 Paul Singer 等捐助者总共向一个超级政治行动委员会捐赠了近 1800 万美元，以支持竞选宾夕法尼亚州美国参议员的共和党人 David McCormick。 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/griffin-schwarzman-fuel-mccormick-super-pac-s-18-million-haul</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 22:46:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
